1
00:00:14,472 --> 00:00:15,392
So pretty.

2
00:00:15,551 --> 00:00:16,232
Yeah.

3
00:00:18,672 --> 00:00:19,672
Let's take a few more.

4
00:00:19,672 --> 00:00:20,311
This spot is great.

5
