Let's take a family photo later.

6
00:00:23,151 --> 00:00:24,092
Cheese.

7
00:00:34,351 --> 00:00:35,371
No, thank you.

8
00:01:13,952 --> 00:01:14,412
Zhi Mei,

9
00:01:22,211 --> 00:01:25,071
