14
00:01:35,812 --> 00:01:37,291
You actually remember that.

15
00:01:38,672 --> 00:01:40,291
That proves I planned it well.

16
00:01:41,772 --> 00:01:42,312
Zhimei,

17
00:01:43,591 --> 00:01:44,231
from now on,

18
00:01:45,091 --> 00:01:45,991
I'll be with you

19
00:01:46,931 --> 00:01:48,231
throughout your life.

20
00:01:50,451 --> 00:01:51,151
Thank you.

21
00:01:51,851 --> 00:01:52,472
You're welcome.

22
00:02:21,371 --> 00:02:22,052
That's it?

23
00:02:23,271 --> 00:02:25,252
Great, really good.

24
00:02:27,791 --> 00:02:28,851
Sorry to interrupt.

25
00:02:28,851 --> 00:02:30,212
I'm a photographer.

26
00:02:30,212 --> 00:02:31,891
You two are so sweet.

27
00:02:31,891 --> 00:02:33,511
Can I take a picture of you?

28
00:02:34,692 --> 00:02:35,271
Sure.

29
00:02:36,652 --> 00:02:37,092
Wu Xi.

30
00:02:38,551 --> 00:02:39,212
I remember

31
00:02:39,872 --> 00:02:41,972
