32
00:02:46,511 --> 00:02:46,752
Zhimei.

33
00:03:00,532 --> 00:03:01,372
Zhimei.

34
00:03:03,312 --> 00:03:05,291
Don't be bothered by those noises.

35
00:03:06,011 --> 00:03:07,972
Just look at me

36
00:03:08,652 --> 00:03:09,712
with your eyes and heart.

37
00:03:10,372 --> 00:03:11,291
I will help you

38
00:03:11,291 --> 00:03:13,092
