42
00:03:34,511 --> 00:03:36,432
has basically been absorbed.

43
00:03:36,992 --> 00:03:38,291
The recovery of your vision

44
00:03:38,291 --> 00:03:39,611
is just a matter of time.

45
00:03:41,312 --> 00:03:42,492
Yes.

46
00:03:45,312 --> 00:03:46,051
Mr. Wu,

47
00:03:46,632 --> 00:03:47,551
the next part

48
00:03:48,132 --> 00:03:51,032
will involve a deep psychological assessment of the patient.

49
00:03:51,331 --> 00:03:52,372
which requires a private discussion.

50
00:03:52,932 --> 00:03:55,092
Please wait outside.

51
00:04:03,391 --> 00:04:04,692
You can go now.

52
00:04:09,492 --> 00:04:10,351
Okay.

53
