Here's the thing.

54
00:04:20,051 --> 00:04:21,391
Based on your description,

55
00:04:22,132 --> 00:04:25,152
you can't recognize the face of the person close to you,

56
00:04:25,632 --> 00:04:26,592
and even firmly believe

57
00:04:27,071 --> 00:04:28,171
that he has been replaced,

58
00:04:28,511 --> 00:04:30,011
accompanied by cognitive biases

59
00:04:30,011 --> 00:04:31,271
towards reality and the world.

60
00:04:31,492 --> 00:04:33,071
These typical characteristics

61
00:04:33,451 --> 00:04:35,292
are consistent with

62
00:04:35,292 --> 00:04:37,492
the rare Capgras delusion after a severe injury.

63
00:04:38,891 --> 00:04:39,451
Impossible.

64
00:04:40,812 --> 00:04:42,571
This is ridiculous.

65
00:04:43,492 --> 00:04:44,372
How is that possible?

66
00:04:45,052 --> 00:04:45,792
I know.

67
00:04:46,132 --> 00:04:47,471
It's hard to accept.

68
00:04:48,651 --> 00:04:50,591
I've been the Ye family's doctor

69
00:04:50,792 --> 00:04:52,992
since the former chairman started his business.

70
00:04:53,732 --> 00:04:54,471
I have no reason

71
00:04:55,031 --> 00:04:56,552
to lie to you.

72
00:04:57,172 --> 00:04:59,091
What you need now

73
00:04:59,091 --> 00:05:00,812
