76
00:05:12,271 --> 00:05:12,771
Dr. Zhang,

77
00:05:13,292 --> 00:05:13,612
how is she?

78
00:05:14,752 --> 00:05:15,852
Let's give her the medication first

79
00:05:15,852 --> 00:05:16,812
and observe the effects.

80
00:05:18,911 --> 00:05:21,091
This is a nerve stabilizer

81
00:05:21,432 --> 00:05:23,292
that can help her vision recover more steadily.

82
00:05:24,992 --> 00:05:25,492
Thank you.

83
00:05:33,271 --> 00:05:33,831
Zhi Mei,

84
00:05:34,692 --> 00:05:35,071
be good,

85
00:05:40,112 --> 00:05:40,732
Take the medicine.

86
00:05:44,471 --> 00:05:45,031
Am I

87
00:05:45,911 --> 00:05:47,752
