88
00:06:01,071 --> 00:06:02,151
Good girl.

89
00:06:07,451 --> 00:06:08,331
Drink some water.

90
00:06:26,132 --> 00:06:28,252
Okay, take a rest.

91
00:06:29,132 --> 00:06:30,252
Lie down.

92
00:06:36,132 --> 00:06:37,372
Take a nap.

93
00:06:37,672 --> 00:06:38,692
I'll be right back.

94
00:07:08,112 --> 00:07:08,792
Mr. Zhou,

95
00:07:09,911 --> 00:07:11,252
I've sung the opera

96
00:07:11,852 --> 00:07:13,091
