100
00:07:19,391 --> 00:07:20,971
it's almost done.

101
00:07:24,331 --> 00:07:25,071
Thank you, Mr. Zhou.

102
00:07:27,771 --> 00:07:28,971
Ye Zhimei

103
00:07:29,151 --> 00:07:31,252
