104
00:07:31,451 --> 00:07:33,471
She's like a lamb to the slaughter.

105
00:07:34,132 --> 00:07:35,612
Not just you people,

106
00:07:35,612 --> 00:07:36,531
even I...

107
00:07:43,951 --> 00:07:44,831
Her name

108
00:07:45,132 --> 00:07:47,232
