112
00:08:00,951 --> 00:08:01,372
Understood.

113
00:08:02,151 --> 00:08:02,292
Understood.

114
00:08:07,911 --> 00:08:09,071
Sir, Madam,

115
00:08:09,071 --> 00:08:10,632
