144
00:10:34,151 --> 00:10:34,712
Zhi Mei.

145
00:10:35,752 --> 00:10:36,651
Zhi Mei!

146
00:10:43,372 --> 00:10:44,092
Zhi Mei!

147
00:10:52,011 --> 00:10:53,511
